# Splunk Query Tester - Cursor Rules
# ============================================================
# FRONTEND RULES (existing)
# ============================================================

## HARD CONSTRAINTS (never violate)
- React 16.13.1. NOT React 17 or 18.
- Use ReactDOM.render(), NEVER createRoot().
- Zustand v4.5.x with default import: import create from 'zustand'
- NEVER use: useId, useDeferredValue, useTransition, startTransition, Suspense for data
- NEVER use MUI (@mui/*). Use @splunk/react-ui + @splunk/themes + styled-components v5.
- NEVER use Tailwind CSS in components. Splunk bundling strips it. Use CSS Modules or styled-components.
- Node.js 18.12. Vite 4.5.x. Closed network - no CDN imports at runtime.
- IDs: crypto.randomUUID()
- Entry point: ReactDOM.render() wrapped in SplunkThemeProvider.

## Architecture
- State: Single Zustand store (testStore.ts) with Immer middleware.
- Only separate hook: useSavedSearches (async data fetching).
- Data hierarchy: Test -> Scenario[] -> TestInput[] -> InputEvent[] -> FieldValue[]
- rowIdentifier at INPUT level (not event level).
- testType: standard | query_only. ValidationType: standard | ijump_alert.
- Each scenario runs independently (no cartesian product).
- TestInput uses inputMode (not inputType), jsonContent as string.
- fileRef stores metadata only (not File object).
- TestDefinition has app field. QueryConfig has spl + savedSearchOrigin (no mode toggle).

## UI Components
- Use @splunk/react-ui for Button, Card, ControlGroup, Select, TextArea, Message, Modal, Switch, Tabs.
- Wrap app in SplunkThemeProvider family=enterprise colorScheme=dark density=comfortable.
- Dark mode. CSS custom properties for colors.
- Progressive horizontal flow: App -> Query -> Data -> Validation -> Results.
- Placeholders on ALL inputs. NO pre-filled default values in UI.
- Payload builder applies fallbacks at submission time only.

## File Organization
- core/types/index.ts - all interfaces and enums
- core/constants/defaults.ts - factory functions (createDefaultTest etc)
- core/constants/limits.ts - MAX_TESTS=20, MAX_SCENARIOS=10, MAX_INPUTS=10, MAX_EVENTS=50, MAX_FIELDS=30
- core/store/testStore.ts - single Zustand v4 store with Immer
- core/store/selectors.ts - memoized selectors
- features/{scenarios,query,validation,results,eventGenerator}/ - feature components
- common/ - shared wrapper components
- api/ - splunkApi.ts, testApi.ts
- hooks/useSavedSearches.ts

## Key Patterns
- addEvent inherits field names from previous event with empty values
- addFieldToAllEvents adds field to every event in an input simultaneously
- JSON editor: debounced store update (300ms) with local state for instant feedback
- Run button: AbortController for cancel, 120s timeout
- Multivalue results: split on newline, render each value on own line
- Pre-flight validation: 8 checks before API call
- Confirmation dialogs: delete test, delete non-empty scenario, clear validation

